# Backend Configuration
# To use a Cloud Database (like Supabase Postgres), uncomment and set the DATABASE_URL below
# Find this in your Supabase Dashboard -> Database -> Connection String -> URI
# Make sure to change [YOUR-PASSWORD] to your actual password.

# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres:[YOUR-PASSWORD]@db.[YOUR-PROJECT-REF].supabase.co:5432/postgres"

# If DATABASE_URL is not set, the app will default to local SQLite finance.db
